::DrillBit/KitKat2/StarScream::

DrillBit thought of other stratagies, because Killfest didn't like his
plan, but was distracted by KitKat and SilverScouts conversation.

"It must have been something with cloning. We are like sisters," said
KitKat2 to SilverScout.

He walked into the room, looking for DrillBit. He sat next to him
listening to KitKat and SilverScout.
"Great DrillBit, that will be one of your In-Laws when you get married.

DrillBit just put his head in his hands.
"Great......"
